    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and independent throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Variable Differential for optimal torque vectoring. Recent mechanical refreshes include rod bearing replacement with VAC-treated bearings and updated throttle actuators, addressing key platform-specific longevity concerns. The chassis remains tight, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound settings. It sits on staggered forged alloys, maintaining excellent unsprung weight characteristics for sharp turn-in and high-speed stability.",
